{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But he admits that he was carrying a 45 Tommy-- what we call a Tommy gun, but that it jammed and he didn't fire.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Like he said in his first article, he was trying to make himself out a great hero to his-- I guess his division commander.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he wrote this long narrative before the investigation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he got caught on it when they came along for the sworn testimony.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But none of them mentioned that Marguerite Higgins was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that was the only reason, in my opinion, that they were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They brought her from the division headquarters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The division record shows that she reported into division headquarters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Doesn't say what happened after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But I'm certain that the only reason that Linden and that small party came there was to permit her to interview the prisoners, but not a word about that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It didn't look good for a commanding general to go out-- or assistant division commander to go out of his area with a nice-looking young babe in somebody else's territory so that she could conduct interviews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But that's the sole reason they were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "There was no other reason for him to be there whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Wasn't in his combat zone at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And Corps backed that up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Corps said-- there's a message of corps says that is 42nd-- 45th division area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "That's in the record.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "When our commanding general complained about 42nd Division being put in there, the message from corps came back, said that is your responsibility.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "That's in your zone of action, not the 42nd Division.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "That's on record.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it isn't in that book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Holocaust Museum in Washington, DC, heard about the records that I have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they want me to mail this to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
